data.description: Welcome home to 1325 14th Avenue, the quintessential turn of the century bungalow. Centrally located near NCMC, UNC Campus, Downtown Greeley, Glenmere Park, HWY-85, 10th St and HWY-34, this home is the perfect place to be. Come up the path to the front door and take in all the charm. Enter the enclosed front porch, through the front door and into the open living room & dining room with original solid wood floors. Signature tall ceilings from the area create spaces filled with light & sunshine. Down the hall, notice the full bathroom and bedroom with a large walk-in closet, rare for the era of home. The kitchen is stocked with modern amenities like an electric range/oven, dishwasher, refrigerator & microwave. The second bedroom looks over the backyard with large windows. The laundry room completes the first level, allowing for one-level living. Downstairs, find storage and room to expand with additional bedrooms, exercise rooms or living areas. The water heater & furnace are new, along with the roof and electrical panel. Out back, notice the large fully fenced back yard is surrounded by mature trees & landscaping. The 2 car detached garage has electricity, and new door springs with remote garage opener. Ready to call home, schedule a showing today and take advantage of this opportunity.
